## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer        | Technology                                      |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| **Frontend** | React 18, Vite, Tailwind CSS, React Router DOM  |
| **Backend**  | Node.js, Express.js, ES Modules                 |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas, Mongoose ODM                     |
| **Auth**     | JWT (JSON Web Tokens), Bcrypt                   |
| **HTTP**     | Axios (centralized instance)                    |
| **Icons**    | Lucide React                                    |
| **File Upload** | Multer                                       |
| **Dev Tools** | Nodemon, Vite HMR                              |

---

## 🔑 Environment Variables

### Frontend — `frontend/.env`

```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
```

### Backend — `server/.env`

```env
PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster.mongodb.net/fittrack
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key_here
NODE_ENV=development
```

---

## 📡 API Endpoints

### Auth Routes — `/api/auth`

| Method | Endpoint             | Access  | Description          |
|--------|----------------------|---------|----------------------|
| POST   | `/register`          | Public  | Register new user    |
| POST   | `/login`             | Public  | Login & get token    |
| GET    | `/profile`           | Private | Get user profile     |
| PUT    | `/profile`           | Private | Update profile       |
| PUT    | `/change-password`   | Private | Change password      |

### Admin Routes — `/api/admin`

| Method | Endpoint              | Access | Description          |
|--------|-----------------------|--------|----------------------|
| GET    | `/members`            | Admin  | Get all members      |
| POST   | `/members`            | Admin  | Add new member       |
| PUT    | `/members/:id`        | Admin  | Update member        |
| DELETE | `/members/:id`        | Admin  | Delete member        |
| GET    | `/users`              | Admin  | Get all users        |
| GET    | `/trainers`           | Admin  | Get all trainers     |
| GET    | `/stats`              | Admin  | Get dashboard stats  |

### Other Routes

| Method | Endpoint                   | Access  | Description          |
|--------|----------------------------|---------|----------------------|
| GET    | `/api/reviews`             | Public  | Get all reviews      |
| POST   | `/api/reviews`             | Public  | Submit review        |
| POST   | `/api/contact`             | Public  | Send contact message |
| GET    | `/api/contact`             | Admin   | View all messages    |
| GET    | `/api/admin/classes`       | Admin   | Get all classes      |
| POST   | `/api/admin/classes`       | Admin   | Create class         |
| GET    | `/api/admin/media`         | Admin   | List media files     |
| POST   | `/api/admin/media/upload`  | Admin   | Upload files         |

